data.description: 2nd Tier level corner lot Table Rock lake Property.  Located on a dead end street this is the perfect place for a weekend home or full time lake living.  The covered porch allows you to enjoy your coffee or evening drinks while listening to the sounds of the lake.  The lake is just a short walking or riding distance down the road as well as access to Joe Bald Park just around the corner. With a detached 2 car garage and an 8 x 12 outbuilding there is plenty storage for your lake toys.   Home is being sold as is.  Owner will make no repairs.
